        "rationale": "Correct."
      },
      {
        "id": "D",
        "text": "16",
        "rationale": "Subtracting the lengths is not the Pythagorean theorem."
      }
    ],
    "correct_choice": "C",
    "explanation": "By the Pythagorean theorem, leg = √(c² − a²) = √(676 − 100) = √576 = 24.",
